<!-- Notification Container -->
<div id="notification" class="notification"></div>

<script>

function showTab(tabNumber) {
// Hide all tab contents
const contents = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content');
contents.forEach(content => content.classList.remove('active'));
// Remove active class from all tabs
const tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab');
tabs.forEach(tab => tab.classList.remove('active'));
// Show selected tab content
const selectedContent = document.getElementById(`tab-${tabNumber}`);
if (selectedContent) {
selectedContent.classList.add('active');
// Reset attribute tabs in the selected content
const attributeTabs = selectedContent.querySelectorAll('.attribute-tab');
const attributeContents = selectedContent.querySelectorAll('.attribute-content');
attributeTabs.forEach(tab => tab.classList.remove('active'));
attributeContents.forEach(content => content.classList.remove('active'));
// Activate first attribute tab
if (attributeTabs.length > 0) {
attributeTabs[0].classList.add('active');
const firstContent = selectedContent.querySelector('.attribute-content');
if (firstContent) {
firstContent.classList.add('active');
}
}
}
// Add active class to clicked tab
event.target.classList.add('active');
}

function showAttributeTab(attributeId) {
// Find the parent item tab content
const itemTabContent = event.target.closest('.item-tab-content');
// Hide all attribute contents in this item tab
const attributeContents = itemTabContent.querySelectorAll('.attribute-content');
attributeContents.forEach(content => content.classList.remove('active'));
// Remove active class from all attribute tabs in this item tab
const attributeTabs = itemTabContent.querySelectorAll('.attribute-tab');
attributeTabs.forEach(tab => tab.classList.remove('active'));
// Show selected attribute content
const selectedContent = document.getElementById(attributeId);
if (selectedContent) {
selectedContent.classList.add('active');
}
// Add active class to clicked attribute tab
event.target.classList.add('active');
// Re-apply active rarity filter for this category
const category = itemTabContent.id.replace('item-tab-', '');
const activeRarityFilter = itemTabContent.querySelector('.rarity-filter.active');
console.log('showAttributeTab - category:', category);
console.log('showAttributeTab - activeRarityFilter:', activeRarityFilter);
if (activeRarityFilter) {
const onclick = activeRarityFilter.getAttribute('onclick');
const matches = onclick.match(/filterByRarity\('([^']+)',\s*'([^']+)'\)/);
if (matches && matches.length >= 3) {
const rarity = matches[2]; // Get the second parameter (rarity)
console.log('showAttributeTab - re-applying rarity filter:', rarity);
filterByRarity(category, rarity, false); // false = don't update button states
} else {
console.log('showAttributeTab - could not parse rarity from onclick:', onclick);
}
} else {
console.log('showAttributeTab - no active rarity filter found');
}
// Re-apply active search filter for this category
const searchInput = itemTabContent.querySelector('.search-input');
if (searchInput && searchInput.value) {
filterGear(category, searchInput.value);
}
}

function filterMods(searchTerm) {
const modItems = document.querySelectorAll('#all-mods .gear-item');
const searchLower = searchTerm.toLowerCase();
console.log('Filtering mods with term:', searchTerm);
console.log('Found mod items:', modItems.length);
modItems.forEach(item => {
const itemNameElement = item.querySelector('.item-name');
const itemSkillElement = item.querySelector('.item-skill');
const itemName = itemNameElement ? itemNameElement.textContent.toLowerCase() : '';
const itemSkill = itemSkillElement ? itemSkillElement.textContent.toLowerCase() : '';
console.log('Item:', itemName, 'Skill:', itemSkill);
// Show item if search term matches name or skill
if (itemName.includes(searchLower) || itemSkill.includes(searchLower)) {
item.style.display = 'flex';
} else {
item.style.display = 'none';
}
});
}
function filterGear(category, searchTerm) {
let gearItems;
if (category === 'consumable') {
// For consumables, search in the specific content area
gearItems = document.querySelectorAll(`#${category}-all .gear-item`);
} else {
// For other categories, use the active attribute tab
const activeAttributeTab = document.querySelector(`#item-tab-${category} .attribute-tab.active`);
if (!activeAttributeTab) return;
const attributeContentId = activeAttributeTab.getAttribute('onclick').match(/'([^']+)'/)[1];
gearItems = document.querySelectorAll(`#${attributeContentId} .gear-item`);
}
const searchLower = searchTerm.toLowerCase();
gearItems.forEach(item => {
const itemNameElement = item.querySelector('.item-name');
const itemSkillElement = item.querySelector('.item-skill');
let itemName = itemNameElement ? itemNameElement.textContent.toLowerCase() : '';
let itemSkill = itemSkillElement ? itemSkillElement.textContent.toLowerCase() : '';
if (searchLower === '' || itemName.includes(searchLower) || itemSkill.includes(searchLower)) {
item.style.display = 'flex';
} else {
item.style.display = 'none';
}
});
}
function updateGameRole(roleValue) {
if (!roleValue) return;
const csrfToken = document.querySelector('[name=csrfmiddlewaretoken]').value;
fetch('/guilds-legacy/player/7/update-game-role/', {
method: 'POST',
headers: {
'Content-Type': 'application/json',
'X-CSRFToken': csrfToken
},
body: JSON.stringify({
'game_role': roleValue
})
})
.then(response => response.json())
.then(data => {
if (data.success) {
// Show success message
showNotification('Role updated successfully!', 'success');
} else {
// Show error message
showNotification('Error updating role: ' + data.error, 'error');
}
})
.catch(error => {
console.error('Error:', error);
showNotification('Error updating role', 'error');
});
}
function showNotification(message, type) {
// Create notification element
const notification = document.createElement('div');
notification.style.cssText = `
position: fixed;
top: 20px;
right: 20px;
padding: 15px 20px;
border-radius: 5px;
color: white;
font-weight: bold;
z-index: 10000;
transition: all 0.3s ease;
${type === 'success' ? 'background: #4CAF50;' : 'background: #f44336;'}
`;
notification.textContent = message;
document.body.appendChild(notification);
// Remove after 3 seconds
setTimeout(() => {
notification.style.opacity = '0';
setTimeout(() => {
document.body.removeChild(notification);
}, 300);
}, 3000);
}
function filterByRarity(category, rarity, updateButtons = true) {
console.log('filterByRarity called - category:', category, 'rarity:', rarity, 'updateButtons:', updateButtons);
// Update active rarity filter button (only if updateButtons is true)
if (updateButtons) {
const rarityFilters = document.querySelectorAll(`#item-tab-${category} .rarity-filter`);
rarityFilters.forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));
if (event && event.target) {
event.target.classList.add('active');
}
}
const activeAttributeTab = document.querySelector(`#item-tab-${category} .attribute-tab.active`);
console.log('filterByRarity - activeAttributeTab:', activeAttributeTab);
if (!activeAttributeTab) {
console.log('filterByRarity - no active attribute tab found');
return;
}
const attributeContentId = activeAttributeTab.getAttribute('onclick').match(/'([^']+)'/)[1];
console.log('filterByRarity - attributeContentId:', attributeContentId);
const gearItems = document.querySelectorAll(`#${attributeContentId} .gear-item`);
console.log('filterByRarity - found gear items:', gearItems.length);
let visibleCount = 0;
gearItems.forEach(item => {
if (rarity === 'all' || item.classList.contains(`rarity-${rarity}`)) {
item.style.display = 'flex';
visibleCount++;
} else {
item.style.display = 'none';
}
});
console.log('filterByRarity - visible items after filtering:', visibleCount);
}
// Initialize filters when DOM is ready
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
console.log('DOM Content Loaded');
// Initialize mod search
const modSearchInput = document.querySelector('.mod-search-input');
if (modSearchInput) {
console.log('Mod search input found and ready');
modSearchInput.addEventListener('input', function() {
console.log('Input event triggered:', this.value);
filterMods(this.value);
});
} else {
console.log('Mod search input not found');
}
// Initialize gear filters for all categories with a small delay
setTimeout(() => {
initializeGearFilters();
}, 100);
// Restore active drifter from session storage
const activeDrifter = sessionStorage.getItem('activeDrifter');
if (activeDrifter) {
// Wait a bit for the page to fully load
setTimeout(() => {
const drifterTab = document.querySelector(`[data-drifter="${activeDrifter}"]`);
if (drifterTab) {
drifterTab.click();
}
// Clear the stored drifter after use
sessionStorage.removeItem('activeDrifter');
}, 500);
}
});
function initializeGearFilters() {
// Only initialize the currently active item tab content
const activeItemTabContent = document.querySelector('.item-tab-content.active');
if (!activeItemTabContent) {
return;
}
const category = activeItemTabContent.id.replace('item-tab-', '');
// Skip mods as they have their own initialization
if (category === 'mod') {
console.log('Skipping mods category');
return;
}
// Skip consumables as they don't have attribute tabs
if (category === 'consumable') {
console.log('Skipping consumables category - no attribute tabs needed');
return;
}
// For weapons, find the first weapon type tab, for others find attribute tab
let activeTab = activeItemTabContent.querySelector('.attribute-tab.active');
console.log('Active tab for', category, ':', activeTab);
// If no active tab found, activate the first one
if (!activeTab) {
console.log('No active tab found for', category, ', activating first tab');
const firstTab = activeItemTabContent.querySelector('.attribute-tab');
if (firstTab) {
// Remove active class from all tabs
const allTabs = activeItemTabContent.querySelectorAll('.attribute-tab');
allTabs.forEach(tab => tab.classList.remove('active'));
// Add active class to first tab
firstTab.classList.add('active');
// Show the corresponding content
const tabId = firstTab.getAttribute('onclick').match(/'([^']+)'/)[1];
const content = document.getElementById(tabId);
if (content) {
// Hide all content first
const allContent = activeItemTabContent.querySelectorAll('.attribute-content');
allContent.forEach(c => c.classList.remove('active'));
// Show the selected content
content.classList.add('active');
}
activeTab = firstTab;
console.log('Activated first tab:', activeTab);
} else {
console.log('No tabs found for', category);
return;
}
}
// Apply "All" rarity filter by default
const allRarityFilter = activeItemTabContent.querySelector('.rarity-filter[onclick*="all"]');
console.log('All rarity filter for', category, ':', allRarityFilter);
if (allRarityFilter) {
// Set the "All" filter as active
const rarityFilters = activeItemTabContent.querySelectorAll('.rarity-filter');
rarityFilters.forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));
allRarityFilter.classList.add('active');
console.log('Applying "All" filter for', category);
// Apply the filter
filterByRarity(category, 'all', false);
} else {
console.log('No "All" rarity filter found for', category);
}
}

// Item Tab Functions
function showItemTab(category) {
// Hide all item tab contents
const contents = document.querySelectorAll('.item-tab-content');
contents.forEach(content => content.classList.remove('active'));
// Remove active class from all item tabs
const tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.right-panel .tab');
tabs.forEach(tab => tab.classList.remove('active'));
// Show selected tab content
document.getElementById(`item-tab-${category}`).classList.add('active');
// Add active class to clicked tab
event.target.classList.add('active');
// Initialize filters for the newly active category (except mods)
if (category !== 'mod') {
setTimeout(() => {
initializeGearFilters();
}, 50);
}
}


// Equip/Unequip Functions
function equipGear(gearItemId, drifterNum, slotType) {
console.log('equipGear called with:', gearItemId, drifterNum, slotType);
// Check if user is staff - this should match Django's user.is_staff
const isStaff = true;
if (!isStaff) {
console.error('Access denied: Staff privileges required');
alert('Access denied: Staff privileges required');
return;
}
const csrfToken = getCookie('csrftoken');
console.log('CSRF Token:', csrfToken);
fetch(`/guilds/player/7/loadout/update/`, {
method: 'POST',
headers: {
'Content-Type': 'application/json',
'X-CSRFToken': csrfToken
},
body: JSON.stringify({
action: 'equip',
gear_item_id: gearItemId,
drifter_num: drifterNum,
slot_type: slotType
})
})
.then(response => response.json())
.then(data => {
if (data.success) {
showNotification(data.message, 'success');
// Store the active drifter before reload
const activeDrifterTab = document.querySelector('.tab.active');
if (activeDrifterTab) {
const drifterNumber = activeDrifterTab.getAttribute('data-drifter');
sessionStorage.setItem('activeDrifter', drifterNumber);
}
setTimeout(() => location.reload(), 1000);
} else {
showNotification(data.error || 'Failed to equip item', 'error');
}
})
.catch(error => {
console.error('Error:', error);
showNotification('Failed to equip item', 'error');
});
}

function unequipGear(gearId) {
// Check if user is staff - this should match Django's user.is_staff
const isStaff = true;
if (!isStaff) {
console.error('Access denied: Staff privileges required');
alert('Access denied: Staff privileges required');
return;
}
fetch(`/guilds/player/7/loadout/update/`, {
method: 'POST',
headers: {
'Content-Type': 'application/json',
'X-CSRFToken': getCookie('csrftoken')
},
body: JSON.stringify({
action: 'unequip',
gear_id: gearId
})
})
.then(response => response.json())
.then(data => {
if (data.success) {
showNotification(data.message, 'success');
// Store the active drifter before reload
const activeDrifterTab = document.querySelector('.tab.active');
if (activeDrifterTab) {
const drifterNumber = activeDrifterTab.getAttribute('data-drifter');
sessionStorage.setItem('activeDrifter', drifterNumber);
}
setTimeout(() => location.reload(), 1000);
} else {
showNotification(data.error || 'Failed to unequip item', 'error');
}
})
.catch(error => {
console.error('Error:', error);
showNotification('Failed to unequip item', 'error');
});
}

// Check if user is staff - this should match Django's user.is_staff

function equipToDrifter(gearItemId, drifterNum, gearType) {
equipGear(gearItemId, drifterNum, gearType);
}

function closeMenu() {
const menu = document.getElementById('drifter-selection-menu');
if (menu) {
console.log('Closing menu');
menu.remove();
} else {
console.log('Menu not found to close');
}
}

// Notification Functions
function showNotification(message, type = 'success') {
const notification = document.getElementById('notification');
notification.textContent = message;
notification.className = `notification ${type} show`;
setTimeout(() => {
notification.classList.remove('show');
}, 3000);
}

// CSRF Token Helper
function getCookie(name) {
let cookieValue = null;
if (document.cookie && document.cookie !== '') {
const cookies = document.cookie.split(';');
for (let i = 0; i < cookies.length; i++) {
const cookie = cookies[i].trim();
if (cookie.substring(0, name.length + 1) === (name + '=')) {
cookieValue = decodeURIComponent(cookie.substring(name.length + 1));
break;
}
}
}
return cookieValue;
}


// Close menu when clicking outside
document.addEventListener('click', function(event) {
// Don't close if clicking on the menu itself or its children
if (event.target.closest('#drifter-selection-menu')) {
return;
}
// Don't close if clicking on equip buttons
if (event.target.closest('.action-btn.equip-btn')) {
return;
}
if (event.target === document.body || event.target.closest('.container')) {
closeMenu();
}
});

function closeDrifterModal() {
const modal = document.getElementById('drifter-selection-modal');
if (modal) {
modal.remove();
}
}

function selectDrifter(drifterSlot, drifterName) {
console.log(`Selecting ${drifterName} for slot ${drifterSlot}`);
// Check if user is staff - this should match Django's user.is_staff
const isStaff = true;
if (!isStaff) {
console.error('Access denied: Staff privileges required');
alert('Access denied: Staff privileges required');
return;
}
// Get the player ID from the URL
const urlPath = window.location.pathname;
const playerId = urlPath.split('/')[3]; // Extract player ID from /guilds/player/{id}/loadout/
// Create form data
const formData = new FormData();
formData.append('drifter_slot', drifterSlot);
formData.append('drifter_name', drifterName);
formData.append('csrfmiddlewaretoken', document.querySelector('[name=csrfmiddlewaretoken]').value);
// Show loading state
const button = event.target;
const originalText = button.textContent;
button.textContent = 'Selecting...';
button.disabled = true;
// Make AJAX request
fetch(`/guilds/player/${playerId}/assign-drifter/`, {
method: 'POST',
body: formData,
headers: {
'X-CSRFToken': document.querySelector('[name=csrfmiddlewaretoken]').value,
}
})
.then(response => {
if (!response.ok) {
throw new Error('Network response was not ok');
}
return response.json();
})
.then(data => {
if (data.success) {
console.log('Drifter assigned successfully');
// Store the active drifter before reload
const activeDrifterTab = document.querySelector('.tab.active');
if (activeDrifterTab) {
const drifterNumber = activeDrifterTab.getAttribute('data-drifter');
sessionStorage.setItem('activeDrifter', drifterNumber);
}
// Reload the page to show the new drifter
window.location.reload();
} else {
throw new Error(data.error || 'Failed to assign drifter');
}
})
.catch(error => {
console.error('Error assigning drifter:', error);
alert(`Error assigning drifter: ${error.message}`);
// Restore button state
button.textContent = originalText;
button.disabled = false;
});
}
// Skill Modal Functions
function showSkillModal(skillName, description, gameId) {
console.log('=== DEBUG SKILL MODAL ===');
console.log('Skill Name:', skillName);
console.log('Description:', description);
console.log('Game ID:', gameId);
console.log('Description length:', description ? description.length : 'null');
console.log('Description type:', typeof description);
const modal = document.getElementById('skill-modal');
const title = document.getElementById('skill-modal-title');
const desc = document.getElementById('skill-modal-description');
const icon = document.getElementById('skill-modal-icon');
if (!modal) {
console.error('Modal element not found!');
return;
}
title.textContent = skillName || 'Unknown Skill';
desc.textContent = description || 'No description available';
// Try to load the icon
const imageBaseUrl = '/static/icons/';
icon.innerHTML = `<img src="${imageBaseUrl}${gameId}.png" alt="${skillName}" style="width: 32px; height: 32px;" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='⚔️'">`;
modal.classList.add('show');
console.log('Modal should be visible now');
}
function closeSkillModal() {
const modal = document.getElementById('skill-modal');
modal.classList.remove('show');
}
// Close modal when clicking outside
document.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
const modal = document.getElementById('skill-modal');
if (e.target === modal) {
closeSkillModal();
}
});
// Fix category counts on page load
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
// Calculate correct counts for each category
const tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab[data-category]');
tabs.forEach(tab => {
const category = tab.getAttribute('data-category');
const categoryContent = document.getElementById(`item-tab-${category}`);
if (categoryContent) {
const items = categoryContent.querySelectorAll('.gear-item');
const countSpan = tab.querySelector('.category-count');
if (countSpan) {
countSpan.textContent = items.length;
}
}
});
});
</script>

<script>
// Edit Name Modal Functions
function openEditNameModal() {
document.getElementById('editNameModal').style.display = 'block';
document.getElementById('newPlayerName').focus();
document.getElementById('newPlayerName').select();
}

function closeEditNameModal() {
document.getElementById('editNameModal').style.display = 'none';
}

// Close modal when clicking outside of it
window.onclick = function(event) {
const modal = document.getElementById('editNameModal');
if (event.target == modal) {
closeEditNameModal();
}
}

// Handle form submission
document.getElementById('editNameForm').addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {
e.preventDefault();
const newName = document.getElementById('newPlayerName').value.trim();
const playerId = window.location.pathname.split('/')[3]; // Extract player ID from URL
if (!newName) {
alert('Please enter a valid name');
return;
}
if (newName === 'Charfire') {
closeEditNameModal();
return;
}
try {
const response = await fetch(`/guilds/player/${playerId}/update-name/`, {
method: 'POST',
headers: {
'Content-Type': 'application/json',
'X-CSRFToken': document.querySelector('[name=csrfmiddlewaretoken]').value
},
body: JSON.stringify({
name: newName
})
});
const data = await response.json();
if (data.success) {
// Update the displayed name
document.querySelector('.header h1').innerHTML = `${newName} <button class="edit-name-btn" onclick="openEditNameModal()" title="Edit player name">✏️</button>`;
// Update page title
document.title = `${newName} - Loadout`;
closeEditNameModal();
alert('Player name updated successfully!');
} else {
alert('Error: ' + data.error);
}
} catch (error) {
console.error('Error updating name:', error);
alert('Error updating name. Please try again.');
}
});
</script>
</body>
</html>
